page.title: 03HOUSING 2
page.content: Since the{1950's}not a lot if any changes have occured to this area. Travelling West from Seaton Carew you come across a patch of land which used to contain delapidated council houses,these were demolished during {1983-84}after standing for about{45 years. Further West you come across more council houses which have recently been modernised.A very small minority of these houses have a garage.They all have central heating with running hot and cold water.The houses have small front and back gardens and the houses are all in short terraces. { Rossmere Ward The houses were built in the{1950's and have medium sized gardens
